68
00:03:19,150 --> 00:03:21,170
was going to launch here in Vancouver.

69
00:03:21,170 --> 00:03:25,720
And so they asked me, Darren, for your part of the research process

70
00:03:25,720 --> 00:03:28,560
we really want that deep dive on the consumer.

71
00:03:28,560 --> 00:03:31,020
What do they think?

72
00:03:31,020 --> 00:03:33,010
And so I built my research team.

73
00:03:33,010 --> 00:03:34,870
And we did a little bit of practice to see

74
00:03:34,870 --> 00:03:36,453
how we could get the best information.

75
00:03:36,453 --> 00:03:40,230
And we learned very quickly that people were a bit uncomfortable

76
00:03:40,230 --> 00:03:42,630
to talk about a product like lingerie.

77
00:03:42,630 --> 00:03:44,380
