84
00:04:07,447 --> 00:04:08,530
knocked down the barriers.

85
00:04:08,530 --> 00:04:11,560
And people were actually very open and actually

86
00:04:11,560 --> 00:04:14,470
had a lot of fun with answering the survey.

87
00:04:14,470 --> 00:04:18,100
And so we were happy to see that when we did the survey,

88
00:04:18,100 --> 00:04:22,330
