00:05:14,190 --> 00:05:16,510
would be interested in their products.

108
00:05:16,510 --> 00:05:20,980
Now, one thing to know about Agent Provocateur is their price point

109
00:05:20,980 --> 00:05:22,070
is very, very high.

110
00:05:22,070 --> 00:05:25,500
