133
00:06:41,220 --> 00:06:44,670
And as you might guess, we found a bimodal result.

134
00:06:44,670 --> 00:06:47,950
So some people were like, yeah, I love it.

135
00:06:47,950 --> 00:06:53,010
And other people were like, no that's not appropriate for here in Vancouver.

136
00:06:53,010 --> 00:06:55,740
The third and, to me perhaps most interesting, thing we

137
00:06:55,740 --> 00:06:58,870
